<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
        
        <template id="calendarplayer" name="Calendar Player">
            <t t-call="web.layout">
                &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
                <html>
                    <head>
                        <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
                        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
                        <title>Gregorian and Mayan Calendar (Long count Calendar) Converter</title>
                        <style>
                            :root {
                                --primary: #2c3e50;
                                --secondary: #e74c3c;
                                --accent: #3498db;
                                --light: #ecf0f1;
                                --dark: #2c3e50;
                                --success: #2ecc71;
                                --warning: #f39c12;
                                --shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                                --radius: 8px;
                            }
                            
                            * {
                                margin: 0;
                                padding: 0;
                                box-sizing: border-box;
                                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                            }
                            
                            body {
                                background-color: #f5f7fa;
                                color: var(--dark);
                                line-height: 1.6;
                                padding-bottom: 70px;
                                width: 100vw;
                                overflow-x: hidden;
                            }
                            
                            header {
                                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--dark));
                                color: white;
                                text-align: center;
                                padding: 1.5rem;
                                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            h1 {
                                font-size: 1.8rem;
                                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                            }
                            
                            .container {
                                width: 100%;
                                margin: 0 auto;
                                padding: 1rem;
                            }
                            
                            .calendar-container {
                                display: flex;
                                flex-direction: column;
                                gap: 2rem;
                                margin-top: 1.5rem;
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            @media (min-width: 768px) {
                                .calendar-container {
                                    flex-direction: row;
                                }
                                
                                .calendar {
                                    flex: 1;
                                }
                            }
                            
                            .calendar {
                                background: white;
                                border-radius: var(--radius);
                                padding: 1.5rem;
                                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            .calendar h2 {
                                color: var(--primary);
                                margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
                                padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
                                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light);
                                display: flex;
                                align-items: center;
                                gap: 0.5rem;
                            }
                            
                            .calendar h2 i {
                                color: var(--accent);
                            }
                            
                            .input-group {
                                margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            .input-group label {
                                display: block;
                                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                                font-weight: 600;
                                color: var(--dark);
                            }
                            
                            .input-row {
                                display: flex;
                                gap: 0.8rem;
                                width: 100%;
                                flex-wrap: wrap;
                            }
                            
                            .input-row input, .input-row select {
                                flex: 1;
                                min-width: 60px;
                            }
                            
                            select, input {
                                padding: 0.8rem;
                                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                                border-radius: var(--radius);
                                font-size: 1rem;
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            .bc-toggle {
                                display: flex;
                                align-items: center;
                                gap: 0.5rem;
                                margin-top: 0.5rem;
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            .toggle-switch {
                                position: relative;
                                display: inline-block;
                                width: 50px;
                                height: 24px;
                            }
                            
                            .toggle-switch input {
                                opacity: 0;
                                width: 0;
                                height: 0;
                            }
                            
                            .slider {
                                position: absolute;
                                cursor: pointer;
                                top: 0;
                                left: 0;
                                right: 0;
                                bottom: 0;
                                background-color: #ccc;
                                transition: .4s;
                                border-radius: 24px;
                            }
                            
                            .slider:before {
                                position: absolute;
                                content: "";
                                height: 16px;
                                width: 16px;
                                left: 4px;
                                bottom: 4px;
                                background-color: white;
                                transition: .4s;
                                border-radius: 50%;
                            }
                            
                            input:checked + .slider {
                                background-color: var(--accent);
                            }
                            
                            input:checked + .slider:before {
                                transform: translateX(26px);
                            }
                            
                            .mayan-cycle {
                                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                                padding: 1rem;
                                border-radius: var(--radius);
                                margin-top: 1.5rem;
                                border-left: 4px solid var(--warning);
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            .mayan-cycle h3 {
                                color: var(--warning);
                                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                            }
                            
                            .cycle-display {
                                font-size: 1.2rem;
                                font-weight: bold;
                                color: var(--dark);
                                text-align: center;
                                padding: 0.5rem;
                                background: white;
                                border-radius: var(--radius);
                                margin-top: 0.5rem;
                            }
                            
                            .today-btn {
                                position: fixed;
                                bottom: 20px;
                                right: 20px;
                                background: var(--success);
                                color: white;
                                border: none;
                                border-radius: 50%;
                                width: 60px;
                                height: 60px;
                                font-size: 1.5rem;
                                cursor: pointer;
                                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                                display: flex;
                                align-items: center;
                                justify-content: center;
                                z-index: 100;
                                transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
                            }
                            
                            .today-btn:hover {
                                transform: scale(1.05);
                                background: #27ae60;
                            }
                            
                            .explanation {
                                margin-top: 1.5rem;
                                font-size: 0.9rem;
                                color: #7f8c8d;
                                line-height: 1.5;
                                width: 100%;
                            }
                            
                            .highlight {
                                color: var(--accent);
                                font-weight: 600;
                            }
                            
                            @media (max-width: 480px) {
                                .input-row {
                                    flex-direction: column;
                                    gap: 0.5rem;
                                }
                                
                                .input-row input, .input-row select {
                                    width: 100%;
                                }
                                
                                .calendar {
                                    padding: 1rem;
                                }
                                
                                h1 {
                                    font-size: 1.5rem;
                                }
                            }
                        </style>
                        
                        <script type="text/javascript" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
                        
                        <script src="https://sdk.minepi.com/pi-sdk.js"></script>
                        
                        <script type="text/javascript">
                            startCommonAppsAI();
                        </script>
                        
                        <div id="blockingOverlay" style="display: flex; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); z-index: 9999; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                            <div style="display: flex; background-color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; color: #333;">
                                <div id="blocking-message" style="display: none;">
                                    <div>
                                        Go to Pi Browser
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <a class="anchor-click" style="color: blue;" href="#" target="_blank">Click here</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div id="paying-message" style="display: none;">
                                    <div>
                                        Donate to unlock Apps
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <a class="anchor-click" style="color: blue;" href="#">Click here</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div t-if="mainnet in ['Mainnet ON', 'Mainnet OFF']">
                                        <br/>
                                        <a id="test_app" style="color: blue;" href="#">Or here to test this app</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div id="loading-message" style="display: block;">
                                    Loading...
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <input type="hidden" id="sandbox" t-att-value="sandbox"/>
                        <input type="hidden" id="mainnet" t-att-value="mainnet"/>
                        <div id="pi_prowser_message" style="display:none;">You need to access from Pi Browser.</div>
                        
                    </head>
                    <body>
                        
                        <div>
                            <style>
                                /* Adjustments for Google Translator to be visible */
                                .goog-te-banner-frame.skiptranslate,
                                .skiptranslate > iframe {
                                    display: none !important;
                                }
                               
                                body {
                                    top: 0px !important; 
                                }

                                .goog-te-menu-frame {
                                    max-width:100% !important; 
                                }
                                .goog-te-menu2 { 
                                    max-width: 100% !important;
                                    overflow-x: scroll !important;
                                    box-sizing:border-box !important; 
                                    height:auto !important; 
                                }
                               
                                /* Hide unwanted elements without hiding the main widget */
                                #goog-gt-tt, 
                                #goog-gt-, 
                                .goog-te-balloon-frame {
                                    display: none !important;
                                } 
                                .goog-text-highlight { 
                                    background: none !important; 
                                    box-shadow: none !important;
                                }
                               
                                .goog-logo-link {
                                    display: none !important;
                                }
                                .goog-te-gadget {
                                    height: 49px !important;
                                    overflow: hidden;
                                }
                            </style>
                            <script type="text/javascript">
                                $( document ).ready(function() {
                                    $("#translate_text_latinchain_2").appendTo(".translate_here");
                                    $("#google_translate_element").appendTo(".translate_here");
                                    
                                    $("#translate_text_latinchain_2").show();
                                    $("#google_translate_element").show();
                                });
                            </script>
                            
                        </div>
                        
                        <header style="justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                            <p class="translate_here" style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 200px; margin-bottom:15px;">
                            </p>
                            <h1 style="text-align:center; color: white !important">
                                <a id="back" href="/" style="color:white !important"><i class="fa fa-step-backward"></i></a>
                            </h1>
                            <h1>Gregorian to Mayan Calendar (Long count Calendar) Converter</h1>
                            <p>Convert dates between Gregorian and Mayan (Long count Calendar) calendars</p>
                        </header>
                        
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="calendar-container">
                                <div class="calendar">
                                    <h2>📅 Gregorian Calendar (Solar Calendar)</h2>
                                    
                                    <div class="input-group">
                                        <label>Year</label>
                                        <div class="input-row">
                                            <input type="number" id="gregorian-year" value="2023" min="1" />
                                            <div class="bc-toggle">
                                                <span>BCE</span>
                                                <label class="toggle-switch">
                                                    <input type="checkbox" id="bc-toggle" checked="true"/>
                                                    <span class="slider"></span>
                                                </label>
                                                <span>CE</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="input-group">
                                        <label>Month</label>
                                        <select id="gregorian-month">
                                            <option value="0">January</option>
                                            <option value="1">February</option>
                                            <option value="2">March</option>
                                            <option value="3">April</option>
                                            <option value="4">May</option>
                                            <option value="5">June</option>
                                            <option value="6">July</option>
                                            <option value="7">August</option>
                                            <option value="8">September</option>
                                            <option value="9">October</option>
                                            <option value="10">November</option>
                                            <option value="11">December</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="input-group">
                                        <label>Day</label>
                                        <input type="number" id="gregorian-day" value="1" min="1" max="31" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="calendar">
                                    <h2>🌄 Mayan Calendar (Long count Calendar)</h2>
                                    
                                    <div class="input-group">
                                        <label>Long Count</label>
                                        <label>Order: baktun.katun.tun.uinal.kin</label>
                                        <h1 id="mayan-format-date"></h1>
                                        <div class="input-row" style="display: none !important;">
                                            <input type="number" id="baktun" placeholder="Baktun" min="0" max="19" value="13" readonly="true"/>
                                            <input type="number" id="katun" placeholder="Katun" min="0" max="19" value="0" readonly="true"/>
                                            <input type="number" id="tun" placeholder="Tun" min="0" max="19" value="0" readonly="true"/>
                                            <input type="number" id="uinal" placeholder="Uinal" min="0" max="17" value="0" readonly="true"/>
                                            <input type="number" id="kin" placeholder="Kin" min="0" max="19" value="0" readonly="true"/>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="mayan-cycle">
                                        <h3>Calendar Cycle</h3>
                                        <p>The Mayan calendar is cyclic. Each cycle consists of 13 Baktuns (approximately 5,125 years).</p>
                                        <div class="cycle-display" id="cycle-display">Current Sun Cycle: 0</div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="explanation">
                                        <p>The Mayan Long Count calendar consists of cycles: <span class="highlight">Baktun</span> (144,000 days), <span class="highlight">Katun</span> (7,200 days), <span class="highlight">Tun</span> (360 days), <span class="highlight">Uinal</span> (20 days), and <span class="highlight">Kin</span> (1 day).</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <button class="today-btn" id="today-btn">📅</button>

                        <script type="text/javascript" src="/website_pinetwork_games_odoo/static/src/js/apps/calendarplayer_functions.js?v=1.110"></script>
                    </body>
                </html>
            </t>
		</template>
        
</odoo>
